{"tid":1661090,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府計劃本年度恢復國歌法二讀辯論","createTime":"2019-10-18T01:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T11:43:02.000Z","uid":212626,"like":10,"dislike":143,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"78daa4560fb3d10e93b8fb3c76c5c5f5db28c098","tid":1661090,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:50:35.000Z","msg":"政制及內地事務局向立法會提交文件表示，特區政府有責任在本地實施《國歌法》，上年度《國歌條例草案》委員會已討論超過50小時，政府計劃在新立法年度恢復二讀辯論，以期盡早通過草案。<br />\n<br />\n至於政制發展討論方面，必須在法理基礎、平和及互信的環境下，以務實態度進行，政府會審時度勢，按《基本法》和人大常委會解釋和決定，推動政制發展。<br />\n<br />\n局方稱，明年4月4日為《基本法》頒布30周年，《基本法》推廣督導委員會將舉辦紀念活動，包括專題展覽和大型研討會等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，當局正就海外有關消除性傾向歧視立法和行政措施，撰寫報告初稿，將會設立溝通平台與持份者作探討。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2278085/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2278085%2F&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=c88176b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2278085/</a>"},{"pid":"4045a44bb6896ecb5d4cbc0967b4c96f2c6e48e8","tid":1661090,"uid":73915,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:51:21.000Z","msg":"天才"},{"pid":"a2694920c2f6a4f6df9510af6b220086bcdfbb5e","tid":1661090,"uid":158090,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:52:46.000Z","msg":"仲黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb80cd4226661779aa293fd4f7140ae06f5f4ce","tid":1661090,"uid":25108,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:53:19.000Z","msg":"玩盡啲<br />\n唱國歌唔流淚直接死刑啦"},{"pid":"727f13253e431d3d9537c7a6efca0d8b89069155","tid":1661090,"uid":256142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:53:21.000Z","msg":"繼續灌火水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1c71f91f6dba8c85bb9f950640360862cc1855","tid":1661090,"uid":37986,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-